00:01:59.670 --> 00:02:02.102
So what I'll do here,
I'll type the word Udacity.

00:02:02.102 --> 00:02:07.039
[BLANK_AUDIO]

00:02:07.039 --> 00:02:11.720
&gt;&gt; Udacity, Wikipedia, the free
encyclopedia page has 346 links,

00:02:11.720 --> 00:02:16.530
16 headings, 4 form controls,
